name: WordRally
skdetail:

Invocation Name: word rally
des:
Challenge Alexa in this fun word pairing game that can be played with family and friends.

Alexa will suggest a random word. It's your job to shout out the first word that comes into your head. Then swap with Alexa and see what she comes up with!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
